                Face Recognition
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                The system verifies the student‚Äôs identity using live face
                recognition.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:space-x-6">
            <div
              class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg"
            >
              3
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex-1 mt-4 md:mt-0 p-6 bg-white border-l-4 border-indigo-600 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition transform hover:scale-105"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700">
                Enter Credentials
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                Students provide their credentials for secure verification.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center md:space-x-reverse md:space-x-6"
          >
            <div
              class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg"
            >
              4
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex-1 mt-4 md:mt-0 p-6 bg-white border-l-4 border-indigo-600 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition transform hover:scale-105"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700">
                OTP Verification
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                A unique OTP is displayed on the teacher‚Äôs projector, entered by
                the student.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 5 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:space-x-6">
            <div
              class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg"
            >
              5
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex-1 mt-4 md:mt-0 p-6 bg-white border-l-4 border-indigo-600 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition transform hover:scale-105"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700">
                Attendance Marked
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                Attendance is confirmed and recorded instantly in the system.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 6 -->
          <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center md:space-x-reverse md:space-x-6"
          >
            <div
              class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-indigo-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg"
            >
              6
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex-1 mt-4 md:mt-0 p-6 bg-white border-l-4 border-indigo-600 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition transform hover:scale-105"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700">
                Teacher‚Äôs Dashboard
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                The updated attendance sheet is available live on the teacher‚Äôs
                portal.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Us Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <!-- Heading -->
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-800 text-center mb-12">
          Get in <span class="text-indigo-600">Touch</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <!-- Contact Form -->
          <div
            class="p-8 bg-white border-l-4 border-indigo-600 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition transform hover:scale-105"
          >
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-6">
              Send Us a Message
            </h3>
            <form class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-gray-600 mb-1" for="name"
                  >Your Name</label
                >
                <input
                  class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-3 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-400 focus:outline-none"
                  type="text"
                  id="name"
                  placeholder="John Doe"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-gray-600 mb-1" for="email"
                  >Email</label
                >
                <input
                  class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-3 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-400 focus:outline-none"
                  type="email"
                  id="email"
                  placeholder="john@example.com"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-gray-600 mb-1" for="message"
                  >Message</label
                >
                <textarea
                  class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-3 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-400 focus:outline-none"
                  id="message"
                  rows="5"
                  placeholder="Type your message..."
                ></textarea>
              </div>
              <button
                type="submit"
                class="w-full bg-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition"
              >
                Send Message
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact Info -->
          <div
            class="p-8 bg-white border-l-4 border-indigo-600 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition transform hover:scale-105"
          >
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-6">
              Reach Us
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              We‚Äôd love to hear from you! Reach out for any questions or
              support.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="text-indigo-600 text-xl mr-3">üìç</span> 123
                Education Street, City, Country
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="text-indigo-600 text-xl mr-3">üìß</span>
                support@smartattendance.com
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="text-indigo-600 text-xl mr-3">üìû</span> +123 456
                7890
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
  </body>
</html>
